### Register
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "password_confirmation": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Logout
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### Add movie to watchlist (by imdb_id)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "imdb_id": "tt0111161"
}

### Add movie to watchlist (by title)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "title": "Poker Face"
}

### Get watchlist
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/watchlist
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get single item
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/watchlist/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update item
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/watchlist/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "status": "watched",
    "user_rating": 9,
    "notes": "Great movie!"
}

### Delete item
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/watchlist/2
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
